      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic pump geometry (identical to COU device) and bovine blood analog. Operating points match the COU envelope. Minor gap: validation experiments used a recirculating loop with a compliance chamber not present in the clinical circuit, introducing a small flow-waveform discrepancy."
